{"tid":2044723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊位連登仔？『我今晚要X死你！』港男被女朋友控告恐嚇！","createTime":"2020-05-31T09:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T09:51:11.000Z","uid":213877,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"64c8af42914db908ecaf010ce5f3a88533e48e88","tid":2044723,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:34:15.000Z","msg":"說話不能亂說，調情也要有個譜。昨日一名港男向在女朋友說『我今晚要X死你！』，懷疑巨有暴力成份，由於女方感到威脅，因而報警求助，該名港男當晚即使被捕，現正接受調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，一名年約30歲的港男，於30日到女朋友的青衣家中晚飯的時候，在閒談中說了『我今晚要X死你』（指性交），女方擔心他有暴力傾向，因而趁他洗澡的時候報警。男方出浴後立刻被捕。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉文指出，情侶之間要留意甜言蜜語的程度，不要情到濃時就亂說話，否則或會足飯法律。他續指，此類個案不常見，而且多數調解了事，但建議大家小心說話。"},{"pid":"dd63cf92c6d5d9d8db2ae7b02385c53cec05df0f","tid":2044723,"uid":63779,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:35:10.000Z","msg":"。。。"},{"pid":"9cd5dae8470dd2433b40a4176eb539c67ffe3eaa","tid":2044723,"uid":200083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0704ab318e7795a3d8df4a36257f5b26c4896d1","tid":2044723,"uid":142775,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"篇野邊到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁短都有咁多錯別字"},{"pid":"55d8347a6960207472f7ab72dfe26742068c97a4","tid":2044723,"uid":70769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我成日咁同老婆講......"},{"pid":"b10ebe7af94e3db47f48af1d9451b266ac60ab8f","tid":2044723,"uid":170383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dae5aa8473e380bd159755019d32e7e90ebbb7","tid":2044723,"uid":12354,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla